# Client-side
<client>
<features>
NTLM
</features>
<server>
http
</server>
 <name>
HTTP with NTLM authorization
 </name>
 <command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/67 -u testuser:testpass --ntlm
</command>
</client>

